label: NetPwrCtrl_UDP_Input_Distribution
info: Collects input from NetPwrCtrl UDP port and distributes into data structure.

name: Receive UDP Trigger and Action Responses
info:
Receives NetPwrCtrl responses from all devices via UDP 7577.
Response is triggered by any action on the device.

name: Split & Index
info: Payload needs to be split by ':' delimiter and then proper index (0-28) is created for the split messages.

name: Split by MAC
info: The unique ID is the MAC Address.

name: Manual UDP Trigger
info: Broadcasts „wer da?“ - String. to NetPwrControl UDP 7575.
